NAF.raw: http : / / www . pba - online . net / boxing / Wladimir - Klitschko - stops - Tony - Thompson - in - 6th - round - to - retain - world - heavyweight - belts / 11614 / Wladimir Klitschko stops Tony Thompson in 6th round to retain world heavyweight belts July 08 , 2012 Wladimir Klitschko stopped Tony Thompson in the sixth round to keep a comfortable hold on his WBA , IBF and WBO heavyweight titles Saturday night . The 36 - year - old champion Klitschko , 58 - 3 with 51 knockouts , floored Thompson with a big right hand near the end of the fifth round at Stade de Suisse , and the 40 - year - old American never recovered . The Ukrainian champion dropped Thompson again in the sixth , and referee Sam Williams gave the challenger a standing count before stopping the fight at 2 : 56 . "Thompson was not so easy to box . I'm satisfied , " Klitschko said . In 2008 , Klitschko stopped Thompson in the 11th round .
